<item>
            <title>[PIG-4219] When parsing a schema, pig drops tuple inside of Bag if it contains only one field</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-4219</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Example&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//We generate a schema object and call toString()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; schemaStr = &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;my_list: {array: (array_element: (num1: &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;,num2: &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;))}&quot;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// Reparsed using org.apache.pig.impl.util.Utils
&lt;/span&gt;Schema schema = Utils.getSchemaFromString(schemaStr);
&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// But no longer matches the original structure
&lt;/span&gt;schema.toString();
&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// =&amp;gt; {my_list: {array_element: (num1: &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;,num2: &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;)}}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
